::Zardus::

Zardus looks at the forest around him, and then at the predacons. It was a 
dangerous situation, if the predacons decided to backstab him, there wouldn't 
be much of a fight.

He looks at Hell Beast and Megatron. "I will invite some of my troops to join 
us also," he says, activating his comm-link.

"Nemesis, Blue Reeker, Hiss, and Breakdown, please join me at my 
coordinates," he says into it, sending them the coordinates.
